data.description: Charming and well maintained 3 bedroom 1.5 bathroom home. This home features granite countertop's in the kitchen and both bathrooms, 42" upper kitchen cabinets, gas range, and wood burning fireplace also has gas. You will find updated vinyl flooring in the living room and two of the bedrooms bedrooms, ceramic tile in the kitchen and both bathrooms, and carpet in the 3rd bedroom (or you could use this room as an office). The garage has been converted into the 3rd bedroom. Enjoy entertaining under the covered patio in the backyard. The Solar Panels and the storage shed in the back yard convey with the home.
